{"tid":991954,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日個恒大同事被人問做咩唔讀ive","createTime":"2019-01-22T19:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T03:17:26.000Z","uid":166877,"like":80,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"87c045a496f520bd8722238f6db0cb77d638758d","tid":991954,"uid":166877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:20:08.000Z","msg":"話說小弟公司有個part time含大仔<br />\n含大未升格之前<br />\n已經係咁同人講自己係大學生<br />\nU life幾精彩<br />\n<br />\n班同事雖然背後恥笑佢<br />\n但喺佢面前都好畀面<br />\n當聽佢打飛機<br />\n<br />\n直到今日 有個80後manager撩佢傾偈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：含大仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：manager<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係喎 你讀邊間U架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我讀恒大架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吓？即係咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：以前A工廠恒商啊 冇咗A-level變咗提供degree課程<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦 即係類似ive啊 咁你做咩唔讀ive啊？都有degree讀 起碼個名好聽啲啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望住個含大仔又嬲但又駁唔到個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲同事即刻忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c82e090f28ba7de5adcca43e6df3846c7cda6f","tid":991954,"uid":202278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:26:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e903a15490714ed6091f075f67a7f5aa8919686f","tid":991954,"uid":175598,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b60ac742935e4e63dff97dead63efbc34f74c535","tid":991954,"uid":134997,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁樣侮辱我地痕大身 出黎隻揪"},{"pid":"0ad4fc0d6380105854d555180d31bcef71cc67bd","tid":991954,"uid":166877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e903a15490714ed6091f075f67a7f5aa8919686f","tid":991954,"uid":175598,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:29:27.000Z","msg":"係囉 禾含都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9595806791450bbab71b9d0beb0682ad8ce3515a","tid":991954,"uid":166877,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:45:39.000Z","msg":"我知到咗今日仲講恒大升格好Out，但有一點不得不說，要多謝含大仔呢part，帶出咗一個近年積咗喺心好耐嘅問題：「喂，點解你可以無知得咁串？」我真係聽過無數次類似嘅說話... 「我真係唔知依間係大學喎」「呢度其實係做咩架」「呢間咩嚟㗎？真係未聽過...」以上嘅說話，在我耳邊聽到嘅時候，都唔係一個問題，而係好有骨咁講... 即最尾唔係「？」而係「！」<br />\n<br />\n細個嘅時候，阿媽、老師都會教，唔識就去學多啲，增值多啲、識多啲嘢、多啲墨水，做個有用嘅人。但而家從大家帶住「！」嘅語氣，背後嘅意思應該係「我唔識你唔係我嘅問題，係你間U唔夠勁令我認識！呢個係你間U嘅錯！」嗱，等我理解一下先，我唔識你間U，係你間U嘅錯，呢個係一套點樣嘅價值觀？一個人要有幾自我膨脹先代入到呢套思想？<br />\n<br />\n我真真實實地聽過，有位80後企喺恒大面前講：「好心啲學店唔好再阻住地球轉啦！」你老，你鍾意讀Kong U、CU係冇問題、好正常，但點解要咁去講一間你口中嘅「學店」？真心，一間「學店」有實力唔追排名而走出嚟繼續畀自由學生同MK妹享受U life，我佩服佢都嚟唔切。點解你唔識佢，就包容唔到佢嘅存在？點解喺我哋不斷追求要有自由、平權嘅年代，我哋對身邊事物嘅包容程度會越來越低？"},{"pid":"de37d57bdad97a8a3a9a75f7cdc3a2cc920d8402","tid":991954,"uid":175598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:51:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1113b31ae421fb093763374c881207658c327726","tid":991954,"uid":90802,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:59:32.000Z","msg":"禾含啲tutor唔會差過兩大囉<br />\n搵我地同哎肥仔比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c50aed662c8d75a5fd4c924bbd61d5b2e95475","tid":99